title: Gritty Fever top Lynx 75-69 in Game 1 of WNBA Finals
text:
> Indiana Gritty Fever top Lynx 75-69 in Game 1 of WNBA Finals Indiana Fever’s Shavonte Zellous, center, hangs on to the ball as Minnesota Lynx’s Rebekkah Brunson, right, and Maya Moore, left, defend in the first half of Game 1 of the WNBA basketball finals Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, in Minneapolis.
